comment: In terms of space, the shop has 2 floors. The lower floor has a bar, without air conditioning, suitable for customers who want to enjoy coffee to prepare for a day at work. The 2nd floor is an air-conditioned room, not too noisy, suitable for choosing as a workplace or also a floor for guests to have more time to enjoy coffee. The space on the 2nd floor is also very beautiful with a view. The street and layout are also good. Service is quite good, there are staff serving at the table. The menu is diverse and the prices are a bit better than other shops I've used, in return the drinks are delicious and to my liking.
